                                                  //| 5 with id = ConnectionManagerId(ubuntu.local,47835)
                                                  //| 14/01/12 13:16:09 INFO storage.BlockManagerMaster: Trying to register Block
                                                  //| Manager
                                                  //| 14/01/12 13:16:09 INFO storage.BlockManagerMasterActor$BlockManagerInfo: Re
                                                  //| gistering block manager ubuntu.local:47835 with
